{% call components.section("Usage") -%}
  <p>Use link with icon to increase the visual interest of a link without using a call to action style. Link with icon can replace links that are used on their own, but not in a paragraph of text.</p>

{%- endcall %}

<hr class="margin-top--2 margin-bottom--10">

{% call components.section("Best practices") -%}

  <p>Don't increase the icon size because the link text size will appear smaller.</p>

  {% call components.example(palette='wrong') %}
